FBIS4-60428 "drnes101_j_94003" FBIS-NES-94-101 Daily Report 25 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Salih Receives King Fahd Reply Cable on 'Id Salih Receives King Fahd Reply Cable on 'Id JN2505054294 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 0330 GMT 25 May 94 JN2505054294 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text of cable from Saudi King Fahd Bin-'Abd-al-'Aziz, custodian of the two holy mosques, to Presidential Council Chairman 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih -- date not given] [Text] His Excellency brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, Presidential Council chairman, Sanaa: I received your congratulations and those of your brothers in the Presidential Council of the fraternal Yemeni people on the occasion of the blessed 'Id al-Adha. I congratulate you on this blessed occasion and ask God Almighty that we all celebrate this occasion next year while enjoying continued happiness and the fraternal Yemeni people and the Islamic nation prosperity and success. Many happy returns. [Signed] Your brother, Fahd Bin-'Abd-al-'Aziz Al Sa'ud, custodian of the two holy mosques and king of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia
